cobblemon_quests_extended.task.actions.t: The deeds the user must perform to fulfill the quest.
The possible Creatures of Poké the user can interact with to fulfill the quest. If the list is empty, any Creature of Poké counts for the quest.
cobblemon_quests_extended.task.amount.to: The quantity of Creatures of Poké.
cobblemon_quests_extended.task.shiny.too: If the Creature of Poké must be shiny to fulfill the quest.
cobblemon_quests_extended.task.genders.t: The possible sexes of the Creatures of Poké.
cobblemon_quests_extended.task.forms.too: The possible forms of the Creatures of Poké (Common, Alolan, Galarian, etc.)
cobblemon_quests_extended.task.pokemon_t: The allowed kinds of the Creatures of Poké (Fire, Water, Grass, etc.)
cobblemon_quests_extended.task.regions.t: The allowed lands of the Creatures of Poké (Kanto, Johto, Hoenn, etc.)
cobblemon_quests_extended.task.pokeballs: The Orb of Capture that the Creature of Poké in question has been or needs to be captured with.
cobblemon_quests_extended.task.dimension: The realms the user must be in to fulfill the quest. (Overworld, Nether, End)
cobblemon_quests_extended.task.biomes.to: The environments the user must be in to fulfill the quest.

The latest hour for the user to fulfill the quest. (non-inclusive)
